      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership price tag? You've got to see this beauty! It's in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car since day one, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. It's super clean, runs perfectly, and is ready for your next adventure. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 42900.0,
