    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a concours-grade E46 M3, representing the zenith of BMW's naturally aspirated S54 inline-six development. This powerplant features individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system, both of which have been recalibrated for optimal timing and volumetric efficiency. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to address known floor pan fatigue and a suspension system utilizing factory-spec Sachs dampers and fresh bushings for original turn-in response. Preventative maintenance is exhaustive, including a documented rod bearing replacement and cooling system overhaul using OE components. This vehicle is mechanically impeccable, offering a visceral driving experience with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
